    <div class="Assessment.name">A Smaller Batch of Lemonade</div>
    <div class="im_statement"><p>When Elena makes lemonade, she usually mixes 9 scoops of lemonade powder with 6 cups of water. Today, she doesn&#x2019;t have enough ingredients.&#xA0;</p>

<p>Think of a recipe that would give a smaller batch of lemonade but still taste the same. Explain or show your reasoning.</p>
</div>
